{"id":10910,"date":"2024-03-09T16:23:38","date_gmt":"2024-03-09T09:23:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10910"},"modified":"2024-03-09T16:23:48","modified_gmt":"2024-03-09T09:23:48","slug":"chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang\/","title":{"rendered":"Chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn chung c\u01b0 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng n\u1eafm r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng <\/span><b>chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf chung c\u01b0.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chung c\u01b0 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10919\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10919\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10919 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-9.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10919\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10919\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-9.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10919\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i \u0110i\u1ec1u 108 c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Nh\u00e0 \u1edf 2014, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec chung c\u01b0 sau khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c. Ph\u00ed n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n giao d\u1ecbch c\u0103n nh\u00e0, ph\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 2% gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kinh ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec chung c\u01b0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0. Khi Nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ban qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb chung c\u01b0, ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng chung c\u01b0 th\u00f4ng qua, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch trong vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10911\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10911\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10911 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-1.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10911\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10911\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-1.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10911\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, nh\u1eefng c\u01b0 d\u00e2n \u1edf chung c\u01b0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed n\u00e0y cao hay th\u1ea5p ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1eebng c\u0103n h\u1ed9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 3.000 &#8211; 5.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u1edf x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c thu nh\u1eadp th\u1ea5p. Th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, an ninh khu v\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t n\u00ean m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5p.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c chung c\u01b0 t\u1ea7m trung m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed s\u1ebd dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 6.000 &#8211; 10.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed7i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 s\u1ebd thu m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m trong h\u1ea1n m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n mua chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0 do Nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf TP.HCM<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10912\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10912\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10912 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-2.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10912\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10912\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-2.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10912\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0 \u1edf TP.HCM<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00ed cho c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chung c\u01b0 do ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong ph\u1ea1m vi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U\u1ef7 ban Nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><b>Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><b>Gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u ( \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2\/th\u00e1ng)<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><b>Gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a ( \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2\/th\u00e1ng)<\/b><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 thang m\u00e1y<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>700<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>5.000<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 thang m\u00e1y<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>1.200<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>16.500<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0 do Nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10913\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10913\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10913 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-3.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10913\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10913\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-3.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10913\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">U\u1ef7 ban Nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng v\u1eeba ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea7n v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 s\u00e0n cho c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chung c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u ( \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2\/th\u00e1ng)<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a ( \u0111\u1ed3ng\/m2\/th\u00e1ng)<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 thang m\u00e1y<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">500<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">3.000<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 thang m\u00e1y<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">1.500<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">6.000<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10914\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10914\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10914 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-4.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10914\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10914\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-4.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10914\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed = M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chung c\u01b0 x Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng thu\u1ef7 c\u0103n h\u1ed9<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng b\u00ean trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ban c\u00f4ng g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m2.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed gi\u1eef xe chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10915\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10915\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10915 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-5.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10915\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10915\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-5.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10915\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed gi\u1eef xe<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed7i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef xe \u1edf chung c\u01b0, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea trung b\u00ecnh ta c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed g\u1eedi xe \u0111\u1ea1p: t\u1eeb 30.000 \u2013 50.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/xe\/ th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed g\u1eedi xe m\u00e1y (d\u01b0\u1edbi 175m3): t\u1eeb 30.000 \u2013 100.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/xe\/ th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed g\u1eedi xe m\u00e1y (tr\u00ean 175m3): t\u1eeb 100.000 \u2013 200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/xe\/ th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed g\u1eedi xe \u00f4 t\u00f4: t\u1eeb 800.000 \u2013 2.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/xe\/ th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec7n, n\u01b0\u1edbc, internet.<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10916\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10916\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10916 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-6.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10916\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10916\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-6.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10916\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec7n, n\u01b0\u1edbc, internet<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed cho c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n, n\u01b0\u1edbc, internet kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n mua chung c\u01b0 m\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec7n sinh ho\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7n nay:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 0- 50: Gi\u00e1 1.388 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 51-100: Gi\u00e1 1.433 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 101- 200: gi\u00e1 1.660 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 201- 300: gi\u00e1 2.082 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 301 \u2013 400: gi\u00e1 : 2.324 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb Kwh 400 tr\u1edf l\u00ean: 2.399 VND<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed n\u01b0\u1edbc sinh ho\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7n nay: 15.000 &#8211; 18.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ m3<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Internet: <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">80.000 &#8211; 400.000 t\u00f9y v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 wifi hay c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh internet.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_10917\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10917\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10917 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-7.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10917\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10917\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-7.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10917\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec7n \u00edch nh\u01b0 Vinhomes, Masteri,.. s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi ph\u00ed k\u00e8m theo nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i: m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed s\u1ebd dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00f9y quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 15.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0 \u2013 30.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed BBQ: kho\u1ea3ng 200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ l\u01b0\u1ee3t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 2 ti\u1ebfng<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>T\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_10918\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10918\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10918 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-8.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10918\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10918\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang-8.jpg\" alt=\"chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10918\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u1edf tr\u00ean ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n chi tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3ng 1.500.000- 4.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng giao d\u1ecbch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i ghi chi ti\u1ebft m\u1ecdi chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ecdc k\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro, tranh ch\u1ea5p sau n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/chi-phi-o-chung-cu-moi-thang\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u00eam ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua ho\u1eb7c thu\u00ea chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;10910&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;0\\\/5 - (0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Chi ph\u00ed \u1edf chung c\u01b0 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau?&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-r